    <content type="html">  
    &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ok5y-jSiz--lgia4pgraLzCqgog=/149x0:1744x1063/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/61445431/Screenshot__8_.0.png" /&gt;



  &lt;p id="c4cvaq"&gt;E-commerce platform Shopify now offers support for AR Quick Look, an &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2018/9/17/17862236/ios-12-review-download-features-update-speed-iphone-ipad-screen-time-notifications-siri"&gt;iOS 12&lt;/a&gt; feature that builds augmented reality support directly into the Safari browser.&lt;/p&gt;
